data.description: This gorgeous 4 bedroom/3.5 bath home is impeccably maintained and sits tranquilly on a gorgeous private .81 acre property in the sought after neighborhood of Airmont. This home has all the extras that you have been looking for w/ a generous kitchen featuring 2 SINKS, 2 OVENS & 2 DISHWASHERS Lovely deck overlooking the serene yard w/ outdoor elevator which is awesome for bringing up groceries etc, 3 oversized large bedrooms w/ 2 updated baths & LAUNDRY ON THE FIRST FLOOR. Downstairs has additional living room w/ fireplace, 4th bedroom, 3rd FULL BATH and access to the 2 car garage - BONUS - 1/2 of which has a subfloor & was previously used for a 5th bedroom & has been reverted back to a garage. Ducts for heat/AC remain making it easy to revert again to a 5th bedroom. Updates galore such as a stunning new gazebo on the back deck to enjoy outdoor living at its best during the spring, summer and fall seasons *NEW ROOF & SIDING & GUTTERS* Don't miss out on the perfect home for your family!
